{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"47a52fc9a4","title":"关于军队支左问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cf960db72a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"47a52fc9a4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"e36a03a692","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"47a52fc9a4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是对增派往温州的六二九九部队的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b1ec911b72","type":"title","text":"关于军队支无问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"e36a03a692","type":"paragraph","text":"小资产阶级当权，大资产阶级就要上台。军队支左有很大好处，就是使军队本身受到教育，他们从实际斗争中会体会到这个问题。支左不仅支革命群众，支左派组织，不仅看到社会各方面存在两条路线斗争，同时也能看到军队里存在两条路线斗争，看到阶级斗争也反映到军队里边，军队通过支左也同样把问题暴露在社会上，从而加强军队，提高我们军队的思想水平，这才是唯物主义辩证法。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"b6a67119d3","type":"paragraph","text":"不能把我们的军队搞乱了，解放军内部的问题，可以一个省一个省地来谈判。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"ef1ee805cb","type":"paragraph","text":"行动要愈快愈好，工作不要太急，要做到家。“","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"}],"page":{"id":"68ae23d0fc","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"47a52fc9a4","start":66,"end":66}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0268303a64","type":"paragraph","text":"小资产阶级当权，大资产阶级就要上台．军队支左有很大好处，就是使军队本身受到教育，他们从实际斗争中会体会到这个问题。支左不仅支革命群众，支左派组织，不仅看到社会各方面存在两条路线斗争，同时也能看到军队里存在两条路线斗争，看到阶级斗争也反映到军队里边，军队通过支左也同样把问题暴露在社会上，从而加强军队，提高我们军队的思想水平，这才是唯物主义辩证法。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"88419c4c52","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自谢富治同志 1967 年 8 月 22 日在北师大讲话）","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"8ca8b9e0e0","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"8f6007c5bb","type":"paragraph","text":"不能把我们的军队搞乱了，解放军内部的问题，可以一个省一个省的来谈判。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"c0ea41d9aa","type":"title","text":"关于军队支左问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"dc3e37157c","type":"paragraph","text":"行动要愈快愈好，工作不要太急，要做到家。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"},{"id":"fd3cb6276d","type":"paragraph","text":"（对增派往温州的 6299 部队指示）","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4"}],"page":{"id":"6c9232d9f6","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"47a52fc9a4","start":623,"end":624}}}},"__N_SSG":true}